      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n<s>先问是不是，再问为什么。</s>法轮功不仅有专门的基地，而且是中国传统风格建筑：<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubmV3eW9ya3Vwc3RhdGUuY29tL3Jlc2l6ZXIvR05TT05xWlUzalBXeS0zLXNUQmZBY0RKLUJJPS8xMjgweDAvc21hcnQvYXJjLWFuZ2xlcmZpc2gtYXJjMi1wcm9kLWFkdmFuY2Vsb2NhbC5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tL3B1YmxpYy9LNlRJWjNDWlVSQU41R0ZJTEJZS0RXU1A3QS5qcGc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.newyorkupstate.com/resizer/GNSONqZU3jPWy-3-sTBfAcDJ-BI=/1280x0/smart/arc-anglerfish-arc2-prod-advancelocal.s3.amazonaws.com/public/K6TIZ3CZURAN5GFILBYKDWSP7A.jpg\">https://www.newyorkupstate.com/resizer/GNSONqZU3jPWy-3-sTBfAcDJ-BI=/1280x0/smart/arc-anglerfish-arc2-prod-advancelocal.s3.amazonaws.com/public/K6TIZ3CZURAN5GFILBYKDWSP7A.jpg</a><br/>\n<br/>\n这是维基百科词条：<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvJUU5JUJFJTk5JUU2JUIzJTg5JUU1JUFGJUJBXyglRTclQkElQkQlRTclQkElQTYp\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BE%99%E6%B3%89%E5%AF%BA_(%E7%BA%BD%E7%BA%A6)\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/龙泉寺_(纽约)</a><br/>\n这是他们官方网站：<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cDovL3d3dy5kcmFnb25zcHJpbmdzLm9yZy8\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://www.dragonsprings.org/\">http://www.dragonsprings.org/</a><br/>\n<br/>\n---<br/>\n补充：评论区有指出龙泉寺是神韵培训基地，不是信徒跪拜的场所。\t\t</div>",
